   "source": [
    "## Get climate data for a specific `ProxyRecord`"
   ]
  },
  {

    "\n",
    "pobj.del_clim()\n",
    "pobj.get_clim(model_tas, tag='model')\n",

    "pobj.get_clim(obs_tas_new, tag='obs')\n",
    "pobj.get_clim(obs_pr_new, tag='obs')"
   ]
